09:06.697 --> 09:08.711
He was always in here.

09:08.855 --> 09:10.503
Working away.

09:11.237 --> 09:12.963
Taking care of us.

09:13.731 --> 09:15.856
I admired him so much.

09:17.045 --> 09:19.650
He always knew how
to balance everything, you know.

09:20.484 --> 09:22.785
His teaching. His research.

09:23.378 --> 09:24.851
You and the kids.

09:25.045 --> 09:26.671
He was a good husband

09:26.946 --> 09:29.943
- and a good man.
- We had a lot of laughs.

09:32.105 --> 09:34.382
Laura,  if there's anything
I can do for you.

09:34.635 --> 09:36.482
