09:44.756 --> 09:47.393
and they had a lawyer
from the company

09:47.488 --> 09:49.233
come over here last night

09:49.818 --> 09:53.902
asking for Harlan's laptop
and all of his files.

09:53.985 --> 09:55.531
That's corporate paranoia.

09:55.616 --> 09:57.612
See, they figure if you sign
a contract with them,

09:57.698 --> 09:59.773
they own you
and your first born.

09:59.965 --> 10:01.642
I didn't give them anything.

10:02.817 --> 10:04.192
It's just...

10:04.566 --> 10:07.641
Harlan was working on
something on his own.

10:07.817 --> 10:09.520
Nights. Weekends.

10:09.676 --> 10:11.333
- What?
- I don't know.

10:12.528 --> 10:15.060
All I know is he said
what he was working on

10:15.195 --> 10:18.310
could be a potential money-maker.
He said even millions.

10:19.735 --> 10:21.793
You should get a lawyer
to take a look at it.

10:21.896 --> 10:23.982
- Isn't your brother?
- He read the contract.

10:24.198 --> 10:27.871
