Norepinephrine, dopamine,

12:15.966 --> 12:17.923
Serotonin,
are gushing out of your brain.

12:18.007 --> 12:20.341
Pressure's going through the roof.
Your heart is racing.

12:20.425 --> 12:22.673
You feel fantastic
and one of these days,

12:22.866 --> 12:25.242
